2. Livornese LL Jr, Dias S, Samel C, et al. Hospital-acquired infection with vancomycin-resistant _Enterococcus faecium_ transmitted by electronic thermometers. Ann Intern Med. 1992; 117(2): 112-6. doi: 10.7326/0003-4819-117-2-112; https://www.acpjournals.org/doi/10.7326/0003-4819-117-2-112.
